# PyDBRepo

Is a simple implementation of the Repository pattern to access data in python, providing extensibility flexibility
and builtin tools to manage databases with this pattern.

## Requirements

- Python >= 3.7
  
### Postgres

- psychopg2-binary
  
### MongoDB

- pymongo
- dnspython

